headline: Travel stocks sink: Expedia leads decline following US visa processing freeze
summary: Investing.com -- Expedia Group (NASDAQ:EXPE) stock fell 5% Wednesday, leading a broader decline in travel stocks after the US State Department announced plans to suspend visa processing for individuals from 75 countries.
